    dc:title "Notes on the spider genus Dysdera Latreille, 1804 (Araneae: Dysderidae) in Central Asia" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5157010>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5157020>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5157024>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5157033>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5157035>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5157040>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5157042> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5157010>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–6. Dorsal habitus of Dysdera subcylindrica (1–2), D. dushengi (3–4) and D. mikhailovi sp. nov. (5–6). 1, 3, 5—male; 2, 4, 6—female. Scale bars=2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5157010/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5157020>
    dc:description "FIGURES 19–24. Prosoma of Dysdera mikhailovi sp. nov. male (19–21) and female (22–24). 19, 22—dorsal; 20, 23—lateral; 21, 24—ventral. Scale bars=1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5157020/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5157024>
    dc:description "FIGURES 25–30. Male palp (25–27) and bulb (28–30) of Dysdera subcylindrica (25, 28–30), D. dushengi (26) and D. mikhailovi sp. nov. (27). 25–28—prolateral; 29—anterior; 30—retrolateral. Scale bars: 25–27=0.5 mm, 28–30=0.2 mm. Ab- breviations: Ap–posterior apophysis, Ax–apex, C–crest, Se–stem of the psembolus, Sp–spine, Te–tegulum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5157024/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5157033>
    dc:description "FIGURES 41–46. Psembolus of Dysdera dushengi (41–43) and bulb of D. mikhailovi sp. nov. (44–46). 41, 44—prolateral; 42, 45—anterior; 43, 46—retrolateral. Scale bars: 41–43=0.15 mm, 44–46=0.2 mm. Abbreviations: Ap–posterior apophysis, Ax–apex, Cm–median crest, Cp–prolateral crest, Cr–retrolateral crest, Se–stem of the psembolus, Te–tegulum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5157033/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5157035>
    dc:description "FIGURES 47–49. Psembolus of Dysdera mikhailovi sp. nov. 47—prolateral; 48—anterior; 49—retrolateral. Scale bars=0.15 mm. Abbreviations: Ap–posterior apophysis, Ax–apex, Cm–median crest, Cp–prolateral crest, Cr–retrolateral crest." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5157035/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5157040>
    dc:description "FIGURES 50–57. Endogyne of D. subcylindrica (50–51), D. dushengi (52–53), D. mikhailovi sp. nov. (54–55) and D. arnoldii (56–57). 50, 52, 54, 56—dorsal; 51, 53, 55, 57—ventral. Scale bars=0.2 mm.Abbreviations: Dd–dorsal arch of the diverticulum, La–lateral arm of the spermatheca, Pd–posterior diverticulum, Sk–stalk of the spermatheca, St–spermateca, Tb–transverse bar of the posterior diverticulum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5157040/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5157042>
    dc:description "FIGURES 58–60. Collecting localities of the studied Dysdera species (58–59) and published records of other Central Asian Dysdera species, except for D. crocata (60). Triangle—Dysdera arnoldii, diamond—D. mikhailovi sp. nov., circle—D. dushengi, square—D. subcylindrica. Black symbols refer to the studied material, white symbols refer to literature-derived data. Some symbols could refer to more than one closely situated localities. The frame of Fig. 59 refers to the content of Fig. 58. The numbers in Fig. 60 refer to the following species: 1—D. aculeata; 2—D. arnoldii; 3—D. brignolii; 4—D. dushengi; 5—D. fedtschenkoi Dunin, 1992; 6—D. ferghanica Dunin, 1985; 7—D. kronebergi Dunin, 1992; 8—D. kugitangica; 9—D. kusnetsovi; 10—D. limitanea; 11—D. nenilini; 12—D. pamirica, 13—D. pococki; 14—D. subcylindrica; 15—D. tartarica; 16—D. tystshenkoi Dunin, 1989; 17—D. zarudnyi; 18—D. zonsteini Dimitrov, 2021; 19—D. mikhailovi sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5157042/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

